metadata.name: Metamorphose
metadata.description: My first open edition represents a promise and a deeper exploration into different methods of AI art generation.  The image represents the initial expression of a theme I've wanted to build on for a while.  My plan is to learn, share, and iterate over the next weeks...maybe a month.. and offer holders a burn for the final piece when it is ready.  Join me on the journey and keep me company at @FyrieNFT on twitter!
